ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's an excellent course of stochastic process. I especially appreciate all the proofs we did in the class. Some proofs are tricky and some are elegant. It's fascinating.sure.
Yes, because it gives a great insight about probabilities in a rigorous and advanced way.
It's a nice class, and it's the first time I look at those common problems in a more accurate and serious mathematical way.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Probably I can use stochastic process in my future research.
I have a better understanding of stochastic process.
It might not directly relate to my research, but it gave me a solid background on probabilities which would be useful with no doubts.
I was thinking it more like the applications in Physics, like the modeling about different processes. Then the class was different, but I learned a lot. So it's an interesting class.
